    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. I noticed a lot of the debate seems to center on the environmental side, though. From a planning perspective, is it generally considered an essential tool for hitting climate goals, or is it still viewed as a controversial or experimental policy?",
      "source": "evaluator"
