    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. You mentioned there's political resistance, but you also called it \"non-negotiable.\" Doesn't that crowd that's worried about the economic impact on working families get a bit dismissed in these discussions? It feels like the conversation moves pretty quickly from \"how do we make this fair\" to \"this is just what needs to happen for the planet.\"",
